<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Learna Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body{
            font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height:1.6;
            background-color:#f4f4f4;
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
        }
        .container{
            max-width:600px;
            margin:auto;
            padding:20px;
            background-color:#fff;
            border-radius:5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video " <%= title %> "</p>
        <p>Please  login to our website  to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Learna</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>